	This module allows you to change the Database and Web Administration FreePBX Password.<br/><br/>
        <img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/view_change_password.png" border="0" width="523px" height="105px" ><br/><br/>
	In Database and Web Administration FreePBX Password text field you must enter the new password.<br/>
	In Password Confirmation text field you must enter again the new password.<br/>
	Then click the “Save” button.<br/><br/>
	Remember that the new password may only contain alphanumeric characters, spaces, or the following: .&amp;-@=_!&lt;&gt;.
	<br /><br />
	In Enable direct access allow to enable or disable the freePBX Non-Embedded. This solves some problems of security.
